# Healthcare CRM — Implementation Plan

## Overview

Build a mobile CRM app for session-based healthcare practitioners using **Flutter** (frontend) + **PocketBase** (backend, self-hosted on Hostinger VPS via Coolify). This plan covers the full project in phases, starting with **Phase 0 (Infrastructure)** and **Phase 1 (Auth & Registration)**.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> We will build and get approval for each phase before moving to the next. This plan covers Phases 0 & 1 in detail. Subsequent phases will be planned after these are implemented and tested.

---

