### 0D. PocketBase Collections (Schema)

These collections will be created in PocketBase admin panel or via migrations:

#### `clinics` collection (Auth type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `name` | text | Clinic/hospital name |
| `username` | text | Unique login username |
| `email` | email | Optional |
| `password` | password | Hashed by PocketBase |
| `bed_count` | number | Available beds for concurrent scheduling |
| `clinic_id` | text | Unique 6-char code for doctor joining |

#### `doctors` collection (Auth type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `name` | text | Doctor's full name |
| `age` | number | Doctor's age |
| `email` | email | Optional |
| `username` | text | Login username |
| `password` | password | Hashed by PocketBase |
| `clinic` | relation → clinics | Nullable (null = individual) |
| `is_primary` | bool | Is this the primary doctor of a clinic? |
| `working_schedule` | json | `[{"day": "Monday", "start": "09:00", "end": "17:00", "break_start": "13:00", "break_end": "14:00"}]` |
| `treatments` | json | `[{"type": "Acupuncture", "duration_min": 30, "fee": 500}]` |
| `share_past_patients` | bool | Share pre-join patient records with clinic |
| `share_future_patients` | bool | Share post-join patients with clinic |

#### `patients` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `full_name` | text | Required |
| `phone` | text | Required |
| `date_of_birth` | date | Optional |
| `address` | text | Optional |
| `emergency_contact` | text | Optional |
| `allergies_conditions` | text | Optional |
| `doctor` | relation → doctors | The treating doctor |
| `clinic` | relation → clinics | Nullable |
| `consent_given` | bool | DPDP consent |
| `consent_date` | date | When consent was given |

#### `appointments` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `patient` | relation → patients | Nullable for call-by (filled later) |
| `doctor` | relation → doctors | Required |
| `clinic` | relation → clinics | Nullable |
| `type` | select | `call_by` or `walk_in` |
| `date` | date | Appointment date |
| `time` | text | Appointment time (HH:mm) |
| `status` | select | `scheduled`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `cancelled` |
| `patient_name` | text | For call-by placeholder |
| `patient_phone` | text | For call-by placeholder |

#### `consultations` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `patient` | relation → patients | Required |
| `doctor` | relation → doctors | Required |
| `notes` | text | Consultation notes |
| `bp_level` | text | Optional |
| `pulse` | number | Optional |
| `charged` | bool | Was client charged? |
| `charge_amount` | number | Fee if charged |
| `photos` | file (multiple) | Compressed images |

#### `treatment_plans` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `patient` | relation → patients | Required |
| `doctor` | relation → doctors | Required |
| `consultation` | relation → consultations | Link to first consultation |
| `treatment_type` | text | e.g., "Acupuncture" |
| `start_date` | date | Plan start date |
| `total_sessions` | number | e.g., 6 |
| `interval_days` | number | Days between sessions |
| `session_fee` | number | Fee per session |
| `status` | select | `active`, `completed`, `paused` |

#### `sessions` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `treatment_plan` | relation → treatment_plans | Required |
| `patient` | relation → patients | Required |
| `doctor` | relation → doctors | Required |
| `session_number` | number | e.g., 1 of 6 |
| `scheduled_date` | date | Auto-calculated |
| `scheduled_time` | text | Time slot |
| `status` | select | `upcoming`, `completed`, `missed`, `cancelled` |
| `notes` | text | Session notes |
| `bp_level` | text | Optional |
| `pulse` | number | Optional |
| `photos` | file (multiple) | Compressed images |
| `remarks` | text | Optional |

#### `audit_logs` collection (Base type)
| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `user` | text | User who performed action |
| `user_role` | text | `clinic` or `doctor` |
| `action` | text | e.g., `viewed_patient`, `created_appointment` |
| `record_id` | text | ID of accessed record |
| `collection` | text | Collection name |
| `timestamp` | autodate | Auto-set |

