## Phase 1: Authentication & Registration (Detailed)

### Auth Component

#### [NEW] [auth_service.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/core/services/auth_service.dart)
- Methods: `loginClinic()`, `loginDoctor()`, `registerClinic()`, `registerDoctor()`, `logout()`, `getCurrentUser()`, `isLoggedIn()`
- Stores auth token in `flutter_secure_storage`
- Determines user role from which collection the auth came from

#### [NEW] [auth_provider.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/providers/auth_provider.dart)
- Riverpod providers wrapping `AuthService`
- `authStateProvider` — streams auth state changes
- `currentUserProvider` — provides current user model

---

### Screens

#### [NEW] [login_screen.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/screens/login_screen.dart)
- Role toggle (Clinic / Doctor) at the top
- Username + password fields
- Login button → validates → calls auth service
- "Register" link → navigates to role selection

#### [NEW] [role_selection_screen.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/screens/role_selection_screen.dart)
- Two large card options: "Register as Clinic" / "Register as Doctor"
- Routes to corresponding registration flow

#### [NEW] Clinic Registration (3-step wizard)
- **Step 1**: Clinic name, username, password, confirm password
- **Step 2**: Number of beds (numeric input with stepper +/-)
- **Step 3**: Primary doctor details (name, age, schedule, treatments) — reuses doctor registration form as a sub-component
- On submit: creates clinic record → creates primary doctor record linked to clinic → auto-login

#### [NEW] Doctor Registration (multi-step)
- **Screen 1**: Name, age, username, password
- **Screen 2**: Working schedule (day selector + time pickers for each day, optional break times)
- **Screen 3**: Treatment selection (checkboxes) + per-treatment duration & fee
- **Screen 4**: Join clinic (enter Clinic ID) or practice individually
- On submit: creates doctor record → if clinic ID provided, links to clinic → auto-login

---

### Models

#### [NEW] [clinic_model.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/models/clinic_model.dart)
- Dart data class mapping to `clinics` collection fields
- `fromRecord()` and `toJson()` methods

#### [NEW] [doctor_model.dart](file:///c:/App Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/models/doctor_model.dart)
- Dart data class mapping to `doctors` collection fields
- Includes `WorkingSchedule` and `TreatmentConfig` sub-models

